value.0: This piecemeal of cloth was crafted by a skilled tailor.

The leftover rags sewn together from the creatures that live in the plagued lands, the cloth has become so saturated with the filth of the land that any who wear it become inured to the diseases that run rampant. They also become peternaturally tough, the toughness of the deadened leather and cloth providing much of the immunities of the denziens of the plagued lands themselves.
This gnarled Duergar has seen many years in Laduguer's service.
